  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为工业物联网场景设计一个架构图，核心是从边缘节点采集数据，经过遥测流处理，最终控制执行器。起点是IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，边缘节点作为数据源。那么数据从EdgeNode流出后，第一站是什么？是直接进入控制器还是先做协议转换？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "数据先进入遥测流，也就是IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream，这里做初步的数据清洗和格式化。然后才到执行器控制器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把这条链路画出来：EdgeNode → TelemetryStream → ActuatorController。接下来ActuatorController后面接什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ActuatorController需要跟PLC逻辑层交互，也就是IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic，这是工业控制的核心决策层。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：ActuatorController到PLC_Logic是单向数据流吗？还是双向的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "目前先画单向，PLC_Logic下发控制指令。但这里有个关键——PLC_Logic触发后会进入一个循环处理逻辑，每次commit都要走一遍完整的子流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "那我建议用一个子图把这个循环包起来，标注为'LOOP FOR EACH COMMIT TO MOVE'。循环内部从PLC_Logic开始，先回到TelemetryStream做二次处理，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，循环里的TelemetryStream是另一个实例，处理的是控制反馈数据。然后进入循环内的ActuatorController，最后到MQTT_Broker做消息发布。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "子图结构已添加：LOOP FOR EACH COMMIT TO MOVE，内部链路是PLC_Logic → TelemetryStream → ActuatorController → MQTT_Broker。循环结束后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "MQTT_Broker发布后，需要再经过一轮TelemetryStream做最终的状态确认，然后回到最开始的EdgeNode，形成闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "闭环结构：Broker → TelemetryStream → EdgeNode。这里有个问题，循环外的TelemetryStream和循环内的是同一个标签，但实际是不同的处理阶段，需要区分吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
