    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "不需要改标签，工业场景里TelemetryStream是通用组件，通过上下文区分即可。但循环外的顺序我再确认下：EdgeNode流出是第一个TelemetryStream，然后ActuatorController，再到PLC_Logic，这个顺序没错吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
