      "utterance": "已修正循环内部链路：PLC_Logic → TelemetryStream → ActuatorController → MQTT_Broker。 Broker出来后连到第三个TelemetryStream，最后回到EdgeNode。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
